def has_unwashed_vegetables():
    # Determine if there are any vegetables that need washing
    symbol dirty_vegetables=exists veg:item: is_food_vegetable(veg) and dirty(veg)
    return dirty_vegetables

def has_uncut_vegetables():
    # Check if there are any vegetables that have not yet been cut
    symbol uncut_vegetables=exists veg:item: is_food_vegetable(veg) and not cut(veg)
    return uncut_vegetables

behavior wash_vegetable(veg:item, sink:item):
    body:
        achieve close_char(char, sink)
        achieve_once inside(veg, sink)
        
        if is_faucet(sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
            achieve_once is_on(faucet)
            
        wash(veg)
        
        if is_faucet(sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
            achieve_once is_off(faucet)

behavior cut_vegetable(veg:item, board:item, knife:item):
    body:
        achieve on(veg, board)
        achieve_once inhand(knife)
        achieve cut(veg)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        if has_unwashed_vegetables():
            bind veg: item where:
                is_food_vegetable(veg) and dirty(veg)
            bind sink: item where:
                is_sink(sink)
            wash_vegetable(veg, sink)
        
        if has_uncut_vegetables():
            bind veg: item where:
                is_food_vegetable(veg) and not cut(veg)
            bind board: item where:
                is_cutting_board(board)
            bind knife: item where:
                is_knife(knife)
            cut_vegetable(veg, board, knife)
